author: Kevin

text: My grandson which lives with us, did a charcoal drawing of Prince the deceased singer/dancer. Prince is one of his grandma's favorite performers. It was an odd size, so I searched the internet for custom framers and found American Frame to be the best choice price, service and customization wise. Thank you American Frame.
